{"tid":141001,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《創世魔刧》討論區","createTime":"2017-03-02T14:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-10T01:50:35.000Z","uid":16672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82d31a95df710c584e35ef799fe65da603315581","tid":141001,"uid":16672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"睇左既巴絲歡迎喺度討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n啲喪屍既化妝我覺得好似求其左少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有少少似陳小春套《生化壽屍》果種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋最尾個結局真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0d43c51813042c84687b3fb9d5847e04fae18f6","tid":141001,"uid":13781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"想知結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f02834a726efdd9f1a13a0ae4a6738dc37c4234","tid":141001,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T03:56:59.000Z","msg":"套野真係好悶, 英國片永遠都係口水多過茶"},{"pid":"8b87a15b9f14c7fe1b34217611eab988972d76a2","tid":141001,"uid":944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"我覺得個結局ok喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反傳統喪屍片"},{"pid":"23fc13b52ad6057127b16564f6117e15234164bf","tid":141001,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:52:23.000Z","msg":"Resident Evil &quot;Alice&quot; + Invasion of Body Snatchers + I Am Legend (小說)<br />\n<br />\n突破唔到廿八日後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好拖好英國味<br />\nHungries啲cg整得算幾好<br />\n著墨講人性，求刺激可繞道<br />\n個女仔智慧高得太離地，完全唔似細路"},{"pid":"d813e9945fca0b54ae3d8730923d75ec3a2c6665","tid":141001,"uid":16672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:51:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心下面有劇透</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">其實點解個女仔要令到全世界變晒喪屍?<br />\n純粹自私想老師永遠陪住佢?</span>"},{"pid":"c9d976f0a02cff3d8e9cf9497612349649a7cf50","tid":141001,"uid":13946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心下面有劇透</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[black]其實點解個女仔要令到全世界變晒喪屍?<br />\n純粹自私想老師永遠陪住佢?[/black]</blockquote><br />\n首先係hungries唔係喪屍<br />\n<br />\n最尾咪講咗只要仲有「正常」人生存，「hungries」同「正常人」之間只會無止境咁打，而第二代hungries同病毒可以共生，係intelligence hungries而唔係淨識咬咬咬，可以當係一個進化過程<br />\n<br />\n假設人類天生就係有近視，如果有隻病毒可以令人天生就冇咗近視，啲眼鏡廠一定會為咗生計追殺呢啲「異類」，但係佢哋先屬於係末來<br />\n<br />\n或者咁睇，初代hungries係物理上hungry，二代hungries係知識上hungry，佢哋唔反抗學習，學完「正常人」嘅知識就可以重建返個地球<br />\n<br />\n所以如果唔令正常人感染只會兩敗俱傷"},{"pid":"2b1b5c7587ed12d4543cbfd5fdce9e539e2fe68d","tid":141001,"uid":17064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"睇完"},{"pid":"91b14842d392710948cd88a53d4019db45ef7f0a","tid":141001,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>套野真係好悶, 英國片永遠都係口水多過茶</blockquote><br />\n睇開英劇《異世奇人》<br />\n黑人角色通常儍更更<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c524407d9265f47ea5c3d6a7e3015cb2228df2","tid":141001,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"Behind the scenes<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=UPIi9QFDIj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUPIi9QFDIj0&d=mLsmOwsyuK9ueWbT6ieOiQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5d364374\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=UPIi9QFDIj0</a>"},{"pid":"fdedbf60088ab8d31f0b78f98ca9f0458947a867","tid":141001,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:09:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得套野還好啦 成班新人類統治地球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ddce6ffb53965120868de1bae90488ebd98d42","tid":141001,"uid":48733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-10T01:50:35.000Z","msg":"我又覺得大橋ok <br />\n<br />\n執行可以再好d"}]}